[h3 id=VariousNotes 
	" Various notes
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Important aspects to the game in no particular order
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" You want as little gas as possible at the end of a race, each bar costs 20 frames on the tally screen
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Slick and Brock (typo in the game, should be block) tires are the only relevant upgrades.  The engines do nothing, and the rain tires only affect oil slicks which are not a problem anyway.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Getting slick tires increases max speed from 170 to 180 on every race except 3.  Getting turbo also does this.  Combining them, or getting 2 turbos gets you to 194 speed, but 194 isn't any faster for some reason
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" You lose your upgrade after the bonus screen, so race 4 is with no upgrades
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" If you run out of gas while invulnerable, you still die.  How mean :(
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Gas seems to just be a function of distance, slowing down, or moving left and right do not affect gas usage
		$LF
	]li
]ul
